planning commission reiterated that china will stick to such 
economic reforms as developing exportoriented industries along the 
coast 
he said private enterprise would continue to play a necessary 
and beneficial supplemental role in the socialist economy but 
added that appropriate restrictions would check the growth of 
private industry 
