have occurred to columbias electrical system but when power was 
turned on tuesday morning there were no problems detected 
the system has to be flexible enough to accept these 
disruptions mccartney said i dont want to downplay the 
problem but i think we are professional enough and flexible enough 
to cope with this one 
columbias crew of five is to deploy a communications satellite 
