vietnam had promised it would have all of its 26000 troops out 
of cambodia by sept 26 and the withdrawal sparked fears that 
cambodia will slide into protracted civil war as government troops 
try to fight the threeparty guerrilla coalition without vietnamese 
help 
vietnams invasion in december 1978 ousted the khmer rouge 
regime which had ruled cambodia since 1975 during that time the 
khmer rouge killed hundreds of thousands practicing a radical 
brand of agrarian communism now the khmer rouge is the strongest 
of the threeparty guerrilla front 
