sales of north americanmade cars and trucks rose 
127 percent in midseptember based on a strong showing by general 
motors corp but at least one analyst wondered how long it could 
go on 
the eight major us automakers said monday they sold cars and 
light trucks at an average daily rate of 37948 during the sept 
1120 period this year compared with a rate of 33670 during the 
same time last year 
gm buyers propelled the companys truck sales up 46 percent and 
