prices of stocks of other entertainment companies 
the deal would be another in a wave of consolidation that has 
swept through the entertainment business in recent years as 
companies have sought to position themselves to compete in 
increasingly accessible global media markets 
columbia sony and cocacola co which owns 49 percent of 
columbias stock each declined comment on the published reports 
that sony was offering between 26 and 28 a share for all of 
columbias common stock columbia had about 111 million common 
